        "description": "Event Name: Deepavali Donation Drive\nConducted by: Rotaract Club of KSSEM (RID 3191)\nDate: 19th October 2025\nVenue: Tiruvannamalai, Tamil Nadu\nParticipants from our club: Rotaract Club of KSSEM\n\nThe Rotaract Club of KSSEM took a heartfelt initiative on the occasion of Deepavali by extending support to a family in Tiruvannamalai, Tamil Nadu. The family had reached out requesting assistance for purchasing new clothes and essential ration items to celebrate the festival with joy and dignity.\n\nUnderstanding their situation, our club took full responsibility and contributed \u20b93000 to help them fulfil their festive needs. The members also ensured that the family successfully utilized the amount to purchase the required items, bringing light and happiness into their home during the festive season.\n\nThis standalone act of kindness reflected the club\u2019s strong commitment to community welfare and compassion. Through this simple yet meaningful gesture, the *\\Rotaract Club of KSSEM aimed to spread the true spirit of Deepavali \u2014 the festival of lights, love, and giving.",
