        "avenues_of_service": "Professional Development",
        "description": "The Mastering the Art of Public Speaking online session, organized by the Rotaract Club of Delhi Rajdhani, RID 3011 in association with the Rotaract Club of Ashoka Artisans, RID 3012, was successfully conducted on 12th October 2025 at 8:00 PM via Google Meet. The session was led by Mr. Kartik Deshwal, a renowned Public Speaking and Debate Mentor, Commerce Educator, and experienced MUN Judge and Delegate.\n\nThe event aimed to help participants overcome stage fear, improve communication confidence, and develop impactful public speaking skills. Through an interactive and engaging format, Mr. Kartik guided attendees on techniques to speak naturally without memorization, maintain strong stage presence, and effectively use body language, voice modulation, and eye contact. Participants also took part in hands-on activities such as storytelling, impromptu speaking, and short interactive drills that boosted their confidence and spontaneity.\n\nThe session encouraged active participation and created a comfortable environment for learning through practice and feedback. Attendees appreciated the speaker\u2019s relatable examples and practical tips on managing nervousness and handling on-stage mistakes.\n\nWith collaboration participation from multiple clubs, the event successfully met its objectives of enhancing communication and leadership skills, leaving participants inspired to speak with clarity, confidence, and purpose.",
